        """

        Phase 1 ( skill): 
        Phase 2 ( skill):  SOP 
          - P1 : 
          - P2 : 
          - P3+ : 
        """
        if not context.skill and not self._active_skill:
            # Phase 1: LLM 
            return get_phase1_tools()

        skill_id = self._active_skill or context.skill

        #  SOP 
        status = self._compute_sop_status(context)

        # 
        # v9.1: SOP  -  SOP 
        # 

        # P1:   
        if status["needs_birth_info"] and not status["has_birth_info"]:
            collect_tool_name = get_skill_collect_tool(skill_id) or "request_info"
            tool_def = ToolRegistry.get_tool_def(collect_tool_name)
            if tool_def:
                logger.info(f"[SOP] P1 :  {collect_tool_name}")
                return [tool_def.to_openai_format()]
            # fallback: 
            logger.warning(f"[SOP]  {collect_tool_name} ")

        # P2:   
        if status["needs_compute"] and not status["has_chart_data"]:
            compute_type = get_skill_compute_type(skill_id) or skill_id
            compute_tool_name = get_skill_compute_tool(skill_id) or f"calculate_{compute_type}"
            tool_def = ToolRegistry.get_tool_def(compute_tool_name)
            if tool_def:
                logger.info(f"[SOP] P2 :  {compute_tool_name}")
                return [tool_def.to_openai_format()]
            # fallback: 
            logger.warning(f"[SOP]  {compute_tool_name} ")

        # P3+:   
        tools = ToolRegistry.get_tools_for_skill(skill_id)
        return tools if tools else get_phase1_tools()","errorCode":8,"isMcp":false,"queryChainId":"6bf2ee09-df32-428e-9d30-e0a3e58c810a","queryDepth":4,"requestId":"req_vrtx_011CXLVePNsosKrcBykDX85a"}
